{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"body":"LIVE-CHECK ATTESTATION (dogfood, 2026-07-13): the deployed auto-lander performed a live rebase-on-behalf-of-uploader + submit end-to-end landing change #618 (https://rebar.solutions.navateam.com/c/rebar/+/618) on main. Evidence: main advanced under #618 after Autosubmit was set, so the bot REBASED it to a fresh Patch Set 3 via POST /changes/{id}/rebase with rebase_on_behalf_of_uploader=true (submitter recorded as 'Rebar Bot Nava'; the original uploader + DCO Signed-off-by + rebar-ticket trailers preserved on PS3, which then earned a fresh Verified+1 and merged). Single-change routing (POST /rebase) exercised live; the rebase:chain multi-member variant is the same on_behalf mechanism exercised by the unit suite (test_multi_member_chain_uses_rebase_chain + on_behalf body assertion). Selection FIFO + classify + routing unit-verified (tests/autolander/test_s2a_*)."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1783931157971652001,"uuid":"c8e7a8b7-8cb2-4fe6-bf6b-4017fb39a13c"}